課程概述 Course Description
       針對一般科學領域的研究，提高學生英語閱讀和聽力之能力及口語表達之能力。 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
Courage to raise hand and express own ideas.Students’ critical thinking and Q & A skill will be provoked and practiced.Develop learners’ speaking fluency.Students’ vocabulary in specific profession will be accumulated. Presentation skills will be developed.Enhance learners’ listening fluency.Pronunciation skills will be demonstrated. 

